[28.010337, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\r\u001b[4A  - Each signer has a \u001b[1mdocumented seed phrase backup\u001b[22m stored offline, physically secured                                                                                  \r\u001b[1B   \r\u001b[2B\u001b[38;5;246m❯ \u001b[39m\u001b[7m \u001b[27m               \u001b[130C                  \r\r\n\u001b[38;5;244m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[39m\r\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[38;5;246mesc\u001b[1Cto\u001b[1Cinterrupt\u001b[130C◐\u001b[1Cmedium\u001b[1C·\u001b[1C/effort\u001b[39m\r\r\n\u001b[?2026l"]
